@startuml
title Phase 1E (Planned) - Performance Score and Visual Report Build

actor Supervisor
participant "Report Viewer / PDF Request" as UI
participant "Reporting API" as API
participant "ReportSummaryService" as ReportSvc
participant "PerformanceScoreService" as ScoreSvc
participant "TrendHistoryService" as TrendSvc
participant "ChartDataBuilderService" as ChartSvc
participant "PDF Renderer" as PDF
database "Operational DB" as DB
collections "Object Storage" as Storage

Supervisor -> UI : Open completed report
UI -> API : Request enriched report
API -> ReportSvc : get report snapshot + enrich visuals

ReportSvc -> DB : load finalized work order/report data
DB --> ReportSvc : summary, inverter records, issues

ReportSvc -> ScoreSvc : calculate or fetch performance score
ScoreSvc -> DB : read supporting visit facts if needed
DB --> ScoreSvc : facts
ScoreSvc --> ReportSvc : score, band, breakdown

ReportSvc -> TrendSvc : fetch historical generation/savings series
TrendSvc -> DB : query prior report snapshots
DB --> TrendSvc : trend data
TrendSvc --> ReportSvc : historical series

ReportSvc -> ChartSvc : build chart-ready data
ChartSvc --> ReportSvc : score bar, inverter bars, trends

ReportSvc -> PDF : render report sections
PDF -> Storage : save generated PDF
PDF --> ReportSvc : pdf reference

ReportSvc --> API : enriched report payload
API --> UI : score + charts + pdf reference

@enduml
